rows.label: tlk42350123_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Gula is the perfect place to live
for Phonexes like us!

rows.label: tlk42350123_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It's full of trees and water, there's so
much to eat, and it's lovely and warm!

rows.label: tlk42350123_01_msg0003
rows.name:
That's what my mum and dad
said, anyway.

rows.label: tlk42350123_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Me, I'm just like...are there places
that aren't like that?
